{% comment %}
Shopify Wishlist
Usage:
- Markup: {%- render 'button-wishlist', product: product -%}
- Place this snippet inside your existing product card snippet
Parameters:
- product: <Shopify product> (required)
  {%- if product.handle != blank -%}
  <button type="button" aria-label="Add to wishlist" button-wishlist class="button-wishlist"
    data-product-handle="{{ product.handle }}">

    {%- render 'icon-heart' -%}
  </button>
  {%- endif -%}
  <style scoped>
    .button-wishlist .icon {
      fill: transparent;
      stroke: #F16523;
      transition: fill 0.3s ease;
    }

    .button-wishlist.active .icon {
      fill: #F16523;
      stroke: #F16523;
    }
  </style>
  {% endcomment %}
  